# Assets Directory

Place files here that will be used in the final output Codex produces.

## When to use

- Templates (HTML, PPT, etc.)
- Images, icons, logos
- Boilerplate code
- Fonts and typography
- Sample documents

## Best practices

1. Only include files that are actually needed
2. Keep file sizes reasonable
3. Use clear, descriptive filenames
4. Organize into subdirectories if needed
